Package meico.app.gui

The GUI code of the meicoApp.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataObject.Interaction
    This method defines an action that is triggered by clicking a radial menu item.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataObject
    This class represents the data objects and provides graphical interface elements for it.
    DataObjectLine
    this represents the parent-child relation of two data objects
    ImageData
    This is a wrapper around image datatype, only for the purpose of integration with the meico GUI, i.e. its visualization as a data object.
    MeicoApp
    This is a standalone application of meico with a graphical user interface.
    Player
    The Player class provides the GUI for audio and Midi playback.
    Schema
    This represents XML schemas in the meico GUI.
    Settings
    This provides some basic style definitions.
    Soundbank
    This represents soundbanks/soundfonts in the meico GUI.
    StatusPanel
    This class creates a status bar.
    TxtData
    This is a wrapper around Javas String datatype and represents a .txt file, only for the purpose of integration with the meico GUI, i.e. its visualization as a data object.
    VerovioGenerator
    This class provides tools to generate Verovio code (for score rendering).
    WebBrowser
    This class creates a WebView if Settings.useInternalWebView is set true.
    Workspace
    This part of the interface will be the place where all the data is shown, dropped, converted, ...
    XSLTransform
    This represents XSL transforms in the meico GUI.

Package meico.app.gui Description

The GUI code of the meicoApp.

Axel Berndt
